Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.49,0:00:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫谷山麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.34,0:00:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高中一年级
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SPR又有人来要求解决几桩奇怪的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.61,0:00:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人说朋友被狐狸附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.09,0:00:15.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人说她的老师突然喊着“有幽灵”而倒下了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.49,0:00:20.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们听说这些事都发生在一个叫汤浅的高中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.19,0:00:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去调查一看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原因不明的离奇事件的描述此起彼伏
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是不得了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.55,0:00:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个学校里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.14,0:00:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大约三个月前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.70,0:00:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了一起事件 老师们不相信一个叫笠井千秋的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.33,0:00:36.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能用超能力扭曲汤匙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而联合起来攻击她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.94,0:00:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒你去死
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.55,0:00:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪的事件好像就是从那以后开始发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.26,0:00:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惠老师也是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.59,0:00:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.84,0:00:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而被其他老师排挤
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.50,0:00:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我非得遭到这样的对待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.15,0:00:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么有不祥的预感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得这学校里发生的事件背后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有巨大的阴影正蔓延开来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.19,0:02:40.90,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,档案 3    {\r}{\u1}{\fs40}下课后的诅咒者{\r}  {\fs35}#2
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:54.33,zhouwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唵苏婆你苏婆　吽缚曰罗吽发吒弱吽梵斛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.14,0:02:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祓除不祥 清洗污垢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.77,0:03:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请安静地享用祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.47,0:03:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聆听并实现我等心中所愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以天父之名祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:11.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请倾听我们的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.90,0:03:18.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.84,0:03:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有记录下明显的温度变化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.10,0:03:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这学校里没有什么灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是事件却实际地发生着
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查明原因之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.43,0:03:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能停止调查
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.11,0:03:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做多少调查都是白费的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.41,0:03:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校舍里到处燃烧着的大量鬼火
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.73,0:03:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一个梦么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是...？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.00,0:04:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住要去在意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.86,0:04:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有不好的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好希望大家快点除完灵回来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:20.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.47,0:04:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井同学
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是有什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.06,0:04:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.65,0:04:33.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人都是你的伙伴？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在干着除灵般的活儿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.74,0:04:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.09,0:04:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和尚 巫女 还有约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.44,0:04:42.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.43,0:04:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说是协助者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原真砂子也是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.70,0:04:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.73,0:04:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然知道她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子是名人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经常上电视
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.29,0:04:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.22,0:04:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个学校里有很多恶灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.58,0:05:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相反
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.46,0:05:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.98,0:05:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:04.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明发生了这么多事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.18,0:05:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.23,0:05:07.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也觉得不对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.67,0:05:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子说看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.17,0:05:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是说难道你看得到？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.55,0:05:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有没有
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是灵能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种东西一开始就看不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.09,0:05:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涉谷先生呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.27,0:05:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是灵能力者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.52,0:05:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.58,0:05:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涉谷先生可以说是灵能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是狩灵师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.58,0:05:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实际上又好像是阴阳师...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阴阳师？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.80,0:05:33.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.03,0:05:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人是阴阳师啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.79,0:05:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井同学？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.99,0:06:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个孩子很明显地可疑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:14.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在打探我们的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说在打探
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.89,0:06:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说她只是有点在意吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.45,0:06:23.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想必也知道自己在被学校里的人所怀疑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是把我们当作新的敌人了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.10,0:06:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道到底怎样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:35.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然听说那个笠井同学以前把汤匙扭弯过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.25,0:06:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连PKLT的能力都有么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PKLT？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.37,0:06:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了麻衣来解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.80,0:06:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PKLT是以念力影响生物的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超能力分成ESP和PK两类
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.13,0:06:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ESP是超感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.84,0:06:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将一般人不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用特殊的能力去了解的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透视和心电感应都是这一类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.13,0:07:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外一方面
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PK是念力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:09.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在脑中想象而使物体移动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.29,0:07:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这又分成PKMT PKST PKLT三类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.28,0:07:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PKST是影响静止物体的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭弯汤匙就是这一类
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.17,0:07:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PKMT是影响运动物体的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,PKLT是像刚才说的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,影响生物体的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.57,0:07:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.21,0:07:38.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么问笠井有没有那个什么东西的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.28,0:07:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解释到这儿还不明白么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.67,0:07:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像话啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.35,0:07:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啊 我很笨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.75,0:07:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说如果她真的下了诅咒了的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:50.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.86,0:07:51.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.13,0:07:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“诅咒你去死”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.62,0:07:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.75,0:07:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.10,0:07:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况下 就是用超能力让人痛苦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:01.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是PKLT
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.39,0:08:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不相信那个孩子有那种程度的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.94,0:08:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说就算是英国的欧里瓦.戴维斯那样有名的超能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够使15公斤的铅块撞击墙面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.12,0:08:17.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也没有PKLT的能力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.03,0:08:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是连扭弯汤匙都做不好的外行人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.69,0:08:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小时候 有一阵很流行超能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.23,0:08:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出现了很多能够弯曲汤匙的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.84,0:08:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果大多数都是欺诈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.01,0:08:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有那么老了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.99,0:08:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.96,0:08:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不提那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.78,0:08:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井相信自己的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.72,0:08:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她认为老师对她的攻击是不正当的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.11,0:08:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.62,0:08:56.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒你去死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件就是从那时开始发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.43,0:09:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个事实
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.90,0:09:05.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能无视
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野老师出了车祸
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.29,0:09:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被送到医院了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.32,0:09:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驾驶时
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.66,0:09:26.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然眼前...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.61,0:09:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那家伙搞的鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.81,0:09:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.85,0:09:36.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.12,0:09:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出学校前我碰到了她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.15,0:09:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她用可怕的表情瞪着我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙在诅咒我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.88,0:09:49.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要咒我死去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.48,0:09:56.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.86,0:09:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么想的 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.76,0:09:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.42,0:10:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但情况是越来越恶化了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.35,0:10:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就这样一筹莫展
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.97,0:10:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然感到心里很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.37,0:10:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.84,0:10:19.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快适可而止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:21.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是超能力还是什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们相信你行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.48,0:10:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以快停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.84,0:10:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我......
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果吉野老师死了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.22,0:10:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是杀人犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.28,0:10:33.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个...算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说的太多的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我们就会被诅咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.06,0:10:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.26,0:10:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那两人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.08,0:10:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要包庇那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产砂老师也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要在意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.37,0:11:03.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.60,0:11:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言语中有生命存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命是照耀人类的光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.48,0:11:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会聚于此吧 诸多的神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.77,0:11:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南无本尊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.73,0:11:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言语中有生命存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次还真是棘手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论田径部的房间 还是那个座位
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.24,0:11:51.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明和事件有关的地方都除灵过了的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那种...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.30,0:11:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:11:59.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个房子里不会也出来什么东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去冲茶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.82,0:12:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.16,0:12:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井的事...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.95,0:12:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答得真快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.16,0:12:23.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点事让我很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.47,0:12:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.62,0:12:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.84,0:12:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候停电
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.90,0:12:33.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘘
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.24,0:12:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.41,0:13:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.42,0:13:09.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.63,0:13:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁来救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.80,0:13:15.92,zhouwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唵苏婆你苏婆吽缚吽发吒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于这儿也出现了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.45,0:13:28.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人一次都没看我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.16,0:13:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直只盯着小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:42.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙的目标是小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.87,0:13:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.35,0:13:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.41,0:13:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是为了这个房间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.60,0:13:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了小恋才出现的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.40,0:13:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天梦里看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.13,0:13:52.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学校里有很多鬼火
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.74,0:13:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙是之中的一个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:56.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说不出自己为什么会知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:58.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是就是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.07,0:13:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.43,0:14:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像血一样的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙只盯着小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.10,0:14:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.14,0:14:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼睛那么红
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:20.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在和那家伙一直对视到早上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.90,0:14:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.96,0:14:22.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣的预感对了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚来我的房间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦移开视线的话就不妙了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:33.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我一整夜都在和她对视
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.18,0:14:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.35,0:14:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也不知道会发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:43.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且把睡着的你叫醒多不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.99,0:14:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了什么事的话你打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.84,0:14:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况不妙的话就会叫你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.77,0:14:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:53.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用担心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.98,0:14:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是笠井同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.50,0:15:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为下诅咒...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个PK什么的是需要很大的力量的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.95,0:15:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是PKLT
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实 要影响这么多人是要很大的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.70,0:15:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井那时候连汤匙都没能扭弯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外 被害者周围出现了灵
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.30,0:15:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单纯的用念力所为解释不通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子是不是做了稻草人偶什么的啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每晚都诅咒大家去死之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.48,0:15:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也不是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.01,0:15:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是稻草人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:43.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是会让被钉子钉到的地方疼痛的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.51,0:15:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是能召唤灵的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.56,0:15:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为稻草人偶而使灵出现...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.31,0:15:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,林
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.19,0:15:55.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这种可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.23,0:15:58.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.17,0:16:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么到现在都没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是咒诅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.30,0:16:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒诅？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.50,0:16:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个学校里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在进行着诅咒人的咒法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.94,0:16:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:13.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.11,0:16:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒诅和灵有什么关系呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.21,0:16:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像稻草人偶那样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.70,0:16:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对人形订钉子的咒术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.98,0:16:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就是从阴阳道传来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了麻衣而简单的解释一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在阴阳道中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.65,0:16:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有种叫“魇魅”的诅咒人的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.37,0:16:35.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是使用人形或者诅咒的人的所有物的咒法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.27,0:16:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所谓稻草人偶就是这魇魅的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稻草人只是单纯表现订钉子的人的怨恨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.59,0:16:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对憎恨的对象是没有伤害的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.56,0:16:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是进行诅咒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过对人形订钉子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托神明和生灵进行咒杀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.52,0:16:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咒杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.11,0:16:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神明和生灵接受了他的请求
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会去咒杀那个对象
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.65,0:17:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒者通过魇魅的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以指使神明和生灵 甚至是恶灵
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:13.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被诅咒的座位
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.58,0:17:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击吉野老师的手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.10,0:17:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个从天花板上出现的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.11,0:17:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是恶灵搞的鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人对与这个学校有关的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:25.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用了魇魅的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.03,0:17:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让恶灵去被诅咒的人身边
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恶灵没有一夜就杀死对方的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能让他一边痛苦一边慢慢的走向死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.89,0:17:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的事情在学校里一件件发生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神经纤细的人就会受影响的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:44.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.90,0:17:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,极端的例子就是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:47.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被狐狸附身的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.82,0:17:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在学校引起了很大的骚动
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.60,0:17:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.22,0:17:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是谁做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.50,0:18:02.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是笠井吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.32,0:18:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.80,0:18:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连绫子也这样说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的超能力被否认并被质问了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.09,0:18:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上保护她的老师都被排挤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.10,0:18:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是那两人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.46,0:18:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真烦人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要包庇那个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.37,0:18:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,产砂老师也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.22,0:18:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以她才那样说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.09,0:18:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诅咒你去死
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.45,0:18:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像她说的去做了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.40,0:18:31.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.16,0:18:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因事故入院的吉野老师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.57,0:18:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是在早会上质问她的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.42,0:18:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,断言不是她的根据是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.62,0:18:45.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不需要什么确定的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:52.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笠井不是犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:57.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是笠井
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.75,0:18:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.20,0:19:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就相信你试试
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万一死了人我可不管了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.71,0:19:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.84,0:19:13.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能放任咒诅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.91,0:19:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和林追查犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请大家去找人形
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.27,0:19:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打破魇魅的方法有两个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把咒诅返还给诅咒者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.61,0:19:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者烧掉他使用的人形
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.37,0:19:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人形会藏在诅咒对象的附近
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.22,0:19:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犯人是跟学校有关的人的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.45,0:19:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很有可能是藏在这学校的某个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.38,0:19:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个地方...你知道这学校有多大么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.86,0:19:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把学校翻过来么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:44.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少 犯人埋下我的人形
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:47.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在我们开始调查的周一之后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.54,0:19:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是周四
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还看得出埋藏的痕迹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.41,0:19:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想做的话就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.76,0:19:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.09,0:20:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:11.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还在上课啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:14.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.56,0:20:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 移动教室啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.55,0:20:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 小恋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.43,0:20:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也不太好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.71,0:20:30.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是人形
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.45,0:20:42.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是这不是针对某个人的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.88,0:20:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是为了诅咒这个座位的所有者
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.58,0:20:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个座位让坐在这儿的人发生事故
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.46,0:20:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以让人认为被诅咒的不是人 而是这桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕田径部的房间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.03,0:20:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是针对特定的个人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.17,0:21:01.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是以田径部全体成员为目标的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地板是混凝土的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.75,0:21:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般是埋在地板下的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.38,0:21:10.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.57,0:21:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有藏在天花板里的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.02,0:21:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.87,0:21:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得好 麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:30.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.80,0:21:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是魇魅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被诅咒的座位和田径部
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个延长线上应该有犯人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.82,0:21:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真砂子！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.09,0:22:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 档案3
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.70,0:23:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下课后的诅咒者  第三章
